  <p>
    The OASIS team is not responsible for the use of the downloaded summaries.
  </p>

  <p>
    OASIS summaries are available for download free of charge. However, it would
    be useful to us and our funders to have some information about who uses the
    summaries, so we can make OASIS an even more informative resource. If you
    are happy to be contacted by the OASIS team for feedback on whether and how
    you have used the summary, please leave your email below. We will not share
    your email with third parties. If you later decide that you would prefer not
